<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.6">
<l>kaṇamā mayilkāḷ kaṇṇapi rāṉṟiruk kōlampōṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṇimā naṭampayiṉ ṟāṭukiṉ ṟīrkkaṭi vīḻkiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>paṇamā ṭaravaṇaip paṟpala kālamum paḷḷikoḷ</l>
<l>maṇavāḷar nammai vaitta paricitu kāṇmiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O musters of big peacocks ! I fall at the feet of you who dance</l>
<l>practising a beautiful, great dance, matching the lustrous beauty of Lord Kṛṣṇa!</l>
<l>This is the honour that the Master—who sleeps at all times on the serpent</l>
<l>with dancing hoods—has bestowed upon us, look!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
